<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate the inoperative zonal dryer system (AMM DDG 21-72-01).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>For forward zonal dryer, using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the DEHUMIDIFIER AC-	FWD circuit breaker and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For aft zonal dryer, using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the DEHUMIDIFIER AC-	AFT circuit breaker and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
